The White House has released a report titled "Donald J. Trump: The Buy American, Hire American President," which highlights President Trump's focus on promoting American manufacturing and strengthening the defense industrial base. The report emphasizes that Trump has not only talked about "Made in the USA" but also implemented it across five dimensions of a comprehensive strategy. The result has been a renaissance in American manufacturing and improved national security. The report can be read and a presentation can be watched through the provided links.